      </sparkle:fullReleaseNotesLink>
      <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[
## Fixed

- Fixed a configuration persistence issue where some Macs could reopen with a blank default config after restart.
- Fixed Start on Login behavior so LocalPorts stays hidden in the menu bar instead of opening its UI on boot.

## Changed

- Moved local config storage to `~/Library/Application Support/LocalPorts/` for a cleaner, non-package folder layout.
- Removed the build number badge from the main popover header.
      ]]></description>
